title: Terms may be changed any time at their discretion, without notice to the user
quoteText: From time to time, we may revise these Terms. You can determine when these Terms were last revised by referring to the “Effective” date at the top. Any changes to these Terms will become effective when we post the updated Terms on our website, and will apply to any order after that time.
